    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Salvis <expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Lucreti<lb break="no" n="2"/>us Floren<lb break="no" n="3"/>tinus <lb n="4"/>Rusticus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aeses</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>conlocavit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is carved over an erased earlier text, after the base had been used also as a fountain. Same text of HD017197; HD067630; HD067631. Datierung: ca. um 355-360 oder 364-367.</p>
            </div>
